OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FITV News reporter Barnaby Papadopulos
OL,8,Fmet one man whose cocaine addiction
OL,9,Fbegan at the age of 15 - and quickly
OL,10,Fspun out of control
OL,12,F"Someone found me in a pool of my own
OL,13,Fblood," John recalls.
OL,15,F"They thought I was dead. And I found
OL,16,Fout that a member of my family ended
OL,17,Fup taking a funeral plan out on me
OL,18,Fbecause they thought I wasn't going to
OL,19,Fget the help I needed."
