OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FOn a beautiful morning in Stranraer,
OL,8,Fenjoying a day off from work, the 20-
OL,9,Fyear-old seemed a world away from the
OL,10,Flife which was spiralling out of
OL,11,Fcontrol just a few years ago. We're
OL,12,Fusing a pseudonym to protect his
OL,13,Fidentity.
OL,15,FHe's been clean for over a year, after
OL,16,Fa habit of taking cocaine
OL,17,Frecreationally morphed into a six gram
OL,18,Fa day addiction.
