OL,7,FHe left school at 16 with "next to no
OL,8,Fqualifications," and daily life began
OL,9,Frevolving around the drug - finding
OL,10,Fit, buying it, taking it, and then
OL,11,Ftrying to find some more.
OL,13,F"Every day, every night, you wouldn't
OL,14,Fsleep for days," he said. "Just always
OL,15,Flooking, always chasing it."
