OL,7,FBut one organisation which spoke to
OL,8,FITV News Border cautioned against
OL,9,Freading too much in to the improved
OL,10,Ffigures for the region.
OL,12,FWithYou, which provides support for
OL,13,Fpeople struggling with drug and
OL,14,Falcohol addiction across the UK, said
OL,15,Freferrals for their services had
OL,16,Fincreased by 136% in Dumfries and
OL,17,FGalloway over the past ten years.
OL,19,F'Real issues' around deprivation, says
OL,20,Fpolicy lead
