OL,7,FThe drug was cited in 479 deaths
OL,8,Facross Scotland in 2023, up from 371
OL,9,Fin 2022.
OL,11,FScottish Health Secretary Neil Gray
OL,12,Fsaid that the level of drug misuse
OL,13,Fdeaths was "hugely concerning".
