OL,7,F"We're taking a wide range of actions
OL,8,Fthrough our #250 million National
OL,9,FMission on drugs, including opening a
OL,10,FSafer Drug Consumption Facility pilot,
OL,11,Fworking towards the opening of drug-
OL,12,Fchecking facilities and widening
OL,13,Faccess to life-saving naloxone," he
OL,14,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,16,F"I believe that National Mission
OL,17,Faction has led to much being achieved
OL,18,Fin a short space of time."
