OL,7,FAfter accessing support John is now in
OL,8,Fwork, and clean. He was keen to
OL,9,Fencourage other people in a similar
OL,10,Fsituation to reach out for help.
OL,12,F"At the time, it doesn't seem like
OL,13,Fanybody does care," he said. "I have
OL,14,Fbeen there.
OL,16,F"Reach out for help before it's too
OL,17,Flate."
